Yankees Beat Mariners, Win First Series In 3 WeeksMets’ Win Streak Ends As They Fall To Oakland AthleticsJordan Spieth Narrowly Avoids Collapse To Capture British Open ChampionshipStarlin Castro Headed Back To Disabled List With Hamstring Injury



 

